responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "09FDFAC048B8C4CE3C57F4BDDCF43329", "The beast can burn! Flaming arrows were the only things that damaged old Timberclaw. Unfortunately, I ran out of torches and had to trot on out of there. I nearly got gobbled, so I swore the beast off. But you, I see victory in you. May Candor bless your arrows and keep your feet fluttering. Safe moons to you. ")
